## Priority Scoring Formula

```
Priority Score = (Impact Ã— Urgency) / Effort

Where:
- Impact: 1-10 (business value)
- Urgency: 1-10 (time sensitivity)
- Effort: 1-10 (implementation cost, inverted)
```

### Impact Weights

| Factor | Weight |
|--------|--------|
| Affects critical path (payment, booking) | +3 |
| Reduces tech debt | +2 |
| Improves DX | +2 |
| Performance improvement | +2 |
| Security fix | +4 |
| Accessibility improvement | +2 |

### Urgency Weights

| Factor | Weight |
|--------|--------|
| Blocking someone | +4 |
| Due date approaching | +3 |
| Regression from recent change | +3 |
| Market pressure (competitor) | +2 |
| Slack mentions >3 | +2 |

### Effort Estimation

| Complexity | Effort Score | Time |
|------------|--------------|------|
| Trivial | 1 | <1 hour |
| Low | 3 | 1-4 hours |
| Medium | 5 | 1-2 days |
| High | 7 | 3-5 days |
| Massive | 10 | >1 week |

